</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:PortugueseFlag1185.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/PortugueseFlag1185.svg/150px-PortugueseFlag1185.svg.png" width="150" height="150" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/PortugueseFlag1185.svg/225px-PortugueseFlag1185.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/PortugueseFlag1185.svg/300px-PortugueseFlag1185.svg.png 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:PortugueseFlag1185.svg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
